===============================================================
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS - Linux

Dependecies:
	* ICL (Image Component Library. Not open source yet. Contact 
	  clebrech@techfak.uni-bielefeld.de for getting the sources. After installing
	  make sure, that the icl.pc file is in your $PKG_CONFIG_PATH.

Building:
	$ make
	$ make installlink

The binaries are placed in the ./application folder.
